{"tid":708601,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［米芝蓮］好運印尼餐廳","createTime":"2018-06-19T12:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T03:40:11.000Z","uid":6352,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"939ef9f7ae36eeb76ca01e38d43b4c94b36a1066","tid":708601,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"此店位於觀塘，在往荃灣紅van站頭附近，位置不算上佳。門口簡單，不仔細看看如何相信是挾著六屆米芝蓮推介的老店。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/195622_b6e39340942b675ac96d31aa207e8631.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F195622_b6e39340942b675ac96d31aa207e8631.png&h=61ddf07c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是日偶爾經過，見派頭十足，便一試究竟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/200024_9098e97e6325727df4d5593a8315685d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F200024_9098e97e6325727df4d5593a8315685d.png&h=2f5b8a90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼黃錦飯：水平上佳，巴東牛肉尤其入味。<br />\n沙嗲串燒（牛）：沙嗲香味濃，肉質都算好。<br />\n<br />\n價錢唔算貴，裝修雖舊但乾淨，有點懷舊感覺。"},{"pid":"8847d6c5a227b84c1155eec8848581ead9473823","tid":708601,"uid":68094,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:11:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdaaee0215ab7da22ea9e0c0fca637904048bae6","tid":708601,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:30:46.000Z","msg":"樓主 打手？"},{"pid":"b7fe40366977277d35b68583c03b3b33c167e770","tid":708601,"uid":179723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:43:18.000Z","msg":"間唔時會同媽媽去食 佢算係keep到水準"},{"pid":"8654f3a1826dcd6f742e60456a1c73a229424b6a","tid":708601,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:50:02.000Z","msg":"呢間好耐囉<br />\n但係味道真係油麻地<br />\n以果個價黎講,唔值"},{"pid":"35dddf93f8a35bdefa9f06efe99f6402ed66bf5e","tid":708601,"uid":56807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"呢間係咪以前佐敦van仔站嗰間？"},{"pid":"363cc9a64c4d91768a2bf5d98451ba491dbfd120","tid":708601,"uid":102745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"呢間好好食嫁，我成日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94281fddc4b7fb95874aa0954dec7031398199e","tid":708601,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8654f3a1826dcd6f742e60456a1c73a229424b6a","tid":708601,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:50:02.000Z","msg":"呢間好耐囉<br />\n但係味道真係油麻地<br />\n以果個價黎講,唔值"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:53:03.000Z","msg":"65一個飯，唔算好貴。你去普通茶記都45-50啦"},{"pid":"8f5e586dc6b0afa981e7213b5257cfdb3a600041","tid":708601,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"好鐘意食巴東牛同串燒 食過tst個間 好乸重味精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9169cf4032fb3c389982cf6e9fd5da522fc721d","tid":708601,"uid":161299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:02:17.000Z","msg":"如果特登去可能會失望<br />\n<br />\n可能口味問題 食完唔覺話好特出"},{"pid":"42ecffffd3a224383916bfc3c580dbd3eb75e74b","tid":708601,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"佐敦好食"},{"pid":"d1a4e5de0d5289eacb067aa4c9b96c4eb6424c39","tid":708601,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"成日搭紅van翻柴灣經過 但係一直無機會試 嗰個位咁靜都做得起應該唔會太差"}]}